name: It's just an apple
description:
' I can resist anything except temptation " - Oscar Wilde

We sometimes crave things that might be leathal to us but surrendering to our temptation is the best way we have to feel alive - artwork by @alice_0n chain 

This piece is also part of a collaborative work by the @nftgodddesses - "The fruit of our Labour" sold on Foundation  09.02.2021 to @ExpansionsPunks - 3543 x 3543 px
